  "baseRefName": "main",
  "body": "## Summary\nAdds the final launch control tower, evidence pack, verification scripts, GitHub Actions, website/media/CRM/API/security checks, and final Go/No-Go reports. The whole surface is **artifact-only, approval-first, and performs no external send**.\n\n> One file for the verdict: [`docs/launch-control/99_FINAL_CONTROL_TOWER_REPORT.md`](docs/launch-control/99_FINAL_CONTROL_TOWER_REPORT.md)\n\n## Includes\n- **Launch Control Tower docs** — `docs/launch-control/00–07` + `99` (scorecard, go/no-go matrix, evidence pack, 30-day war room, daily command center, failure playbook, founder checklist, final report).\n- **Master verification script** — `scripts/final_launch_control_verify.py` (44 checks).\n- **Final launch workflow** — `.github/workflows/final-launch-control.yml` (+ commercial-draft-factory, media-social-calendar, site-commercial-verify).\n- **400+ draft factory** — `scripts/commercial_generate_400_drafts.py` (every draft `send_allowed=false`).\n- **Safety audit + commercial readiness** — `commercial_safety_audit.py`, `commercial_launch_readiness.py`.\n- **Media/social planning + verify** — `media_social_calendar_generate.py`, `media_social_verify.py`, ads readiness gate.\n- **Website static QA** — `site_launch_static_check.py` + `docs/site-launch/100_SITE_MANUAL_QA_CHECKLIST.md`.\n- **CRM schema verify** — `commercial_crm_schema_verify.py` + `config/crm_pipeline_schema.json`.\n- **API static check** — `api_commercial_static_check.py` + `docs/ops/API_COMMERCIAL_LAUNCH_QA.md`.\n- **Secret/risk scan** — `final_secret_and_risk_scan.py`.\n- **Final evidence artifacts** — `outputs/commercial_launch/`, `outputs/media_social/`, `outputs/final_launch_control/`.\n- **Tests** — 14 files / 25 tests.\n- README updated with the **Commercial Launch OS** section; clone URL → `Dealix-sa/dealix.git`.\n\n## Safety\n- No external sending · no SMTP · no messaging/cold outreach automation · no professional-network automation · no website auto-submit · no scraping.\n- No secrets; workflows are `permissions: contents: read`, artifact-only.\n- No sensitive data collected before agreement; no unproven claims.\n\n## Tests Run (real)\n```\n$ python -m pytest -q tests/test_commercial_*.py tests/test_media_social_*.py \\\n    tests/test_final_launch_control_verify.py tests/test_site_launch_static_check.py \\\n    tests/test_crm_schema_verify.py tests/test_api_commercial_static_check.py \\\n    tests/test_final_secret_and_risk_scan.py\n25 passed\n\n$ python scripts/final_launch_control_verify.py\n[final-verify] OVERALL PASS — drafts=400, critical_failures=0   # 44/44 checks\n\n$ cd apps/web && npm run typecheck && npx next build\ntypecheck exit 0 · build exit 0 (/robots.txt + /sitemap.xml routes built)\n```\n\n## Final Go/No-Go\n**GO** — public website launch · commercial positioning · 400 review-only drafts · founder manual review · media/social planning · manual social posting · paid diagnostics · discovery calls · proposal creation · pilot planning.\n\n**NO-GO** — automated email sending · cold messaging automation · professional-network automation · website form auto-submit · bulk sending · paid ads live launch without tracking/compliance · external sending from GitHub Actions · processing sensitive data before agreement.\n\nhttps://claude.ai/code/session_01P7HtoCti4Vn31mUaFUAwWs\n\n---\n_Generated by [Claude Code](https://claude.ai/code/session_01P7HtoCti4Vn31mUaFUAwWs)_",
